{"tid":1448112,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［全民討論］民間擺免警隊嘅可能性","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:23:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T02:39:34.000Z","uid":167192,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"96451f573d503fdf1a7fa353ac8236366c6e1768","tid":1448112,"uid":167192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:23:49.000Z","msg":"2019年8月11日，香港警察向廣大市民展示咗一個清晰嘅訊息，就係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢地唔撚會再受到法律規管。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而家想全能嘅連登仔一齊討論，分享大家各行各業嘅專業意見，搵出<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">由市民聯動發起擺免警隊嘅可能性</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如今警隊公信力全失，正正係升級到全民不信任運動嘅最好時機<br />\n<br />\n聽落好似好無稽，但係即管嘗試put our brain together and make it happens.<br />\n諗下721時警隊嘅無恥，諗下今日嘅血海深仇⋯⋯<br />\n佢地無任何資格擁有公權力<br />\n<br />\n要做到呢一步，必須要有bargaining power<br />\n<br />\n可以係:<br />\n1. 全罷 (交稅/課/學）<br />\n2. ？？<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊努力令呢個idea可以成真⋯⋯<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真係好撚嬲呀屌你老母死黑警!!!!!!</span></span>"},{"pid":"c9a006c3303431364996bb994a1a50bb99409519","tid":1448112,"uid":22362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:24:42.000Z","msg":"前線如果夠人 唔該大嗌還拖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1447759\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1447759</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cbeb65f31de269e364ad9c6e75a3db116f178a94","tid":1448112,"uid":171395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:25:10.000Z","msg":"唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvBTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=d966b474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvBTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=025d5939\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"6ea4272168249b7969c06aa92642c04304740a97","tid":1448112,"uid":14652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:25:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">停止勇武抗爭<br />\n一係癱瘓機埸<br />\n一係永久罷工<br />\n一係民陣三百萬遊行</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日發動全民罷工，直至仆街政府跪低為止</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">7.21<br />\n元朗 警黑合作<br />\n8.11<br />\n尖沙咀 開槍爆眼<br />\n銅鑼灣 狗扮示威者混入捉人，非人道拘捕，大力禁示威者傷囗湧出更多血<br />\n葵芳 站內催淚彈開槍<br />\n北角 警黑合作，<br />\n太古 推人落電梯，近距離開槍射殺</span>"},{"pid":"0a961621758f4ba6a838be56c7139216bdea2ad3","tid":1448112,"uid":194894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:25:27.000Z","msg":"稅唔好罷，交多一蚊就得"},{"pid":"5e1fc3a1f10df4d1de351000ca2dec7ebca533c5","tid":1448112,"uid":69087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:25:30.000Z","msg":"立即解散警隊！！"},{"pid":"5de393762e5f8c4359bd53853f3e7e7d55826f57","tid":1448112,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:25:32.000Z","msg":"拒絕承認警隊合法性<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全民抗爭 背水一戰</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">對港鐵不合作運動全民跳閘</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.勇武轉入地下打狗<br />\n2.和理非要癱瘓機場</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為受傷被捕兄弟討回公道</span></span><br />\n<br />\n前線太多手足比捉 一定要升級癱瘓機場 全民打狗 選擇一個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1445481\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1445481</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ee3fac82cdaa64d205649fd646594acd398ee29b","tid":1448112,"uid":67303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:27:57.000Z","msg":"警隊根本係個失控嘅組織 已經唔受任何野規管 想點就點 <br />\n想投訴？唔好話冇number呀 有又點 一樣告唔入<br />\n現時警隊已經冇任何認受性 一定要罷免佢"},{"pid":"52299de421e123ecb66c1f0b77eb4e5396586b4f","tid":1448112,"uid":167192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:29:55.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"cc32c4cf4b5ea9b3d4f1d2c1d7b6756dcfe30d70","tid":1448112,"uid":67303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:36:39.000Z","msg":"推推推推推推推"},{"pid":"c692c4fb573cec7816a45562923b404a3f1bd2f7","tid":1448112,"uid":279095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:38:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bd17bf74a75b2ebacdc3358e8e5271557f98480b","tid":1448112,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:39:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}